web20mash (1.2) unstable; urgency=low

  New features:
    * Some people do a yet another rest called "mashing out rest", so
      add this one as well
    * Also add an alert for the last chance to do an iodine test
      before enzymes are disabled by lautering temperature
    * Add a simple simulation/demo mode
    * Make daemon to drop privileges if run as root

 -- Sven Geggus <sven-deb@geggus.net>  Wed, 07 Nov 2012 23:14:36 +0100

